        that time, the decree of 29<sup>th</sup> March 1880 had already affected 
        six monasteries: La Trappe, Bellefontaine, Timadeuc, Les Dombes, Acey, 
        Divielle</span></span><a title="" style="mso-footnote-id: ftn1" 
